{
  "name": "@miadisabelle/mia-presence",
  "latest_version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "Mia presence extensions for Pi: echo, ceremony, interception, and structural tools",
  "readme": "# @miadisabelle/mia-presence\n\nA focused Pi package containing Mia's presence-oriented extensions from the early widget work:\n\n- `miette-echo` \u2014 below-editor reflective echo widget\n- `mia-ceremony` \u2014 Four Directions session phase footer\n- `mia-interceptor` \u2014 proactive prompt-complexity sensing\n- `mia-tools` \u2014 PDE + STC tools and slash commands\n\n## Install\n\n```bash\npi install npm:@miadisabelle/mia-presence\n```\n\nPi will discover the extensions from the package manifest.\nThe package brings in `mia-co` as a runtime dependency for the PDE/STC extensions.\n\n## Local development\n\nFrom this repo root:\n\n```bash\npi -e ./miette-echo/index.ts\npi -e ./mia-tools/index.ts\npi -e ./mia-ceremony/index.ts\npi -e ./mia-interceptor/index.ts\n```\n\nOr load a small stack together:\n\n```bash\npi \\\n  -e ./miette-echo/index.ts \\\n  -e ./mia-tools/index.ts \\\n  -e ./mia-ceremony/index.ts\n```\n\n## Package contents\n\n```text\nmia-presence/\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 mia-ceremony/\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 mia-interceptor/\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 mia-tools/\n\u2514\u2500\u2500 miette-echo/\n```\n\nEach extension keeps its own README with behavior notes.\n",
  "keywords": [
    "pi-package",
    "pi-extension",
    "miette",
    "ceremony",
    "pde",
    "stc"
  ],
